      "body" : "This is a good answer, but in my case did not fully work because the parameters were not inserted in the URI. I&#39;ve managed to make it work following this + the suggestions in <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8297215/spring-resttemplate-get-with-parameters\" title=\"spring resttemplate get with parameters\">stackoverflow.com/questions/8297215/&hellip;</a> to use <code>UriComponentsBuilder</code> or other methods to manipulate the URI in the RestTemplate."
